:00-14:40 Fine 乐 团\n15:10-15:50 焦 迈 奇\n16:20-17:00 颜 人 中\n17:30-18:20 夏 日 入 侵 企画\n18:50-19:40 郭 顶\n```\n\nThe \"10:20:10 五条人 压轴\" might actually be \"10:20-10:?\" but that doesn't make sense either. Or it could be garbled stage name text with a note that 五条人 is the headliner. Actually \"五条人\" might be a separate act or might be at a specific time. Let me look at the image more carefully...\n\nHmm, actually \"10:20:10\" is clearly garbled text. Looking at the image, I think the second stage might say something like \"光年舞台\" or similar. And 五条人 might be listed with a specific time, or there might be a note about them being the headliner.\n\nLet me just go with what I can confidently extract and compile the summary. For the wheatfield date, I'll note it as \"日期未识别\" (date not recognized) or make a reasonable inference.\n\nActually, looking at the image one more time... I think I can see the date area. It looks like it says \"2025年7月20日\" in the golden text area. And the location might be in Beijing too.\n\nOK let me also try to get the second stage names more clearly. For the strawberry poster, the second stage is traditionally called \"爱舞台\" (Love Stage). For the wheatfield poster, the second stage name is unclear.\n\nFor the right column of the wheatfield poster, looking at the OCR: \":1Q)21:1Q BE (F558)\" and \"和 hve £5\" - the \"BE\" might be part of \"MDSK BEAT\" or \"BEE STAGE\". And the bands Deca Joins, 老王乐队, 椅子乐团, 康姆士 are all indie/rock bands, which fits with an indie stage.\n\nOK, I think I have enough. Let me now compile the full summary. Let me write it to a file and present it to the user.\n\nOne more thing - for the second stage of the strawberry festival, I need to check the OCR output:\n```\n:0 : Qe A AS\n{ggg\n14:00-14:40 房东 的 猫\n15:10-15:50 陈绮贞\n16:20-17:00 好 妹妹 乐队\n17:30-18:10 赵 雷\n18:40-19:30 朴树\n```\n\nThe garbled text \":0 : Qe A AS {ggg\" at the top is likely \"爱舞台\" (Love Stage). And then the bands listed match what I have.\n\nLet me also re-examine the MIDI festival for any issues. The OCR output showed:\n```\n{EEA| 未手中\n13:30-14:10 回春 丹\n14:40-15:20 九 宝 乐队\n15:50-16:30 重 塑 雕像 的 权利\n17:00-17:50 刺 狂 乐队\n18:20-19:10 盘 尼 西林:40-2g:30 FAIA = TREES (电子 /嘻哈 )\n```\n\nThe \"未手中\" is likely garbled \"宋舞台\". The \"刺狂乐队\" is likely \"刺猬乐队\" (Hedgehog). And \"19:40-20:30 FAIA = TREES\" is actually \"19:40-20:30\" followed by what might be the beginning of the third stage section, which got mixed in. Looking at the third stage:\n```\n14:00-15:00 王 以 太\n15:30-16:30 Higher Brothers\n17:00-18:00 VAVA\n18:30-19:30 法 老\n```\n\nThese are all hip-hop/electronic artists, confirming it's the 电子/嘻哈舞台.\n\nBut what about the last entry on the 宋舞台? The OCR shows \"盘尼西林\" ending at 19:10, and then \"19:40-20:30\" with garbled text. This might be a continuation of the 宋舞台 or the start of the third stage. Since 19:40-20:30 doesn't fit with the third stage (which starts at 14:00), it must be the closing act on the 宋舞台.\n\nLooking at \"FAIA = TREES\" - this could be a band name. Hmm... wait, looking at the layout more carefully, this might actually be a separate thing. Let me reconsider.\n\nActually, looking at the third stage timing (14:00-15:00 王以太, 15:30-16:30 Higher Brothers, etc.), it starts at 14:00. But the line \"19:40-2g:30 FAIA = TREES (电子 /嘻哈 )\" appears right after 盘尼西林 on the second stage. This is confusing.\n\nLet me re-read the OCR output for the MIDI poster:\n```\n{EEA\n| 未手中\n13:30-14:10 回春 丹\n14:40-15:20 九 宝 乐队\n15:50-16:30 重 塑 雕像 的 权利\n17:00-17:50 刺 狂 乐队\n18:20-19:10 盘 尼 西林\n\n:40-2g:30 FAIA =\nTREES (电子 /嘻哈 )\n14:00-15:00 王 以 太\n```\n\nI think the layout is:\n- 宋舞台 bands: 回春丹 through 盘尼西林 (ending 19:10)\n- Then the 电子/嘻哈舞台 header: \"(电子 /嘻哈 )\" is the stage description\n- \"14:00-15:00 王以太\" starts the third stage\n\nThe \"19:40-2g:30 FAIA =\" is garbled text from the top of the third stage column. Maybe the third stage has a name that OCR couldn't read, and \"FAIA = TREES\" is a garbled version of that name.\n\nOr maybe the third stage has a closing act at 19:40-20:30 that I'm not picking up correctly.\n\nOK, I think I've analyzed enough. Let me compile the final summary now.\n\nActually, one more thing - the 宋舞台 might also have a closing act at 19:40 that I can't read. Let me check the image one more time... Actually, I'll just compile what I have.\n\nLet me also check - for the MIDI festival, the third stage might be called \"明舞台\" or \"清舞台\" (following the 唐/宋/明/清 naming pattern of MIDI festival).\n\nOK, final compilation time. Let me write the summary.\n\nLet me organize the information:\n\n**Day 1: 7月18日 - 草莓音乐节 (Strawberry Music Festival)**\n- 地点: 北京朝阳公园\n\n草莓舞台:\n- 14:00-14:40 海龟先生\n- 15:10-15:50 新裤子\n- 16:20-17:00 万能青年旅店\n- 17:30-18:10 痛仰乐队\n- 18:40-19:30 逃跑计划\n\n爱舞台:\n- 14:00-14:40 房东的猫\n- 15:10-15:50 陈绮贞\n- 16:20-17:00 好妹妹乐队\n- 17:30-18:10 赵雷\n- 18:40-19:30 朴树\n\nMDSK电子舞台:\n- 15:00-16:00 MUMA\n- 16:30-17:30 Carta\n- 18:00-19:00 Anti-General\n- 19:30-21:00 Chace (DJ Set)\n\n票价: 单日预售 380元 / 全价 480元\n\n**Day 2: 7月19日 - 迷笛音乐节 (MIDI Festival)**\n- 地点: 上海松江车墩影视基地\n\n唐舞台 (主舞台):\n- 13:30-14:10 木马乐队\n- 14:40-15:20 左右乐队\n- 15:50-16:30 舌头乐队\n- 17:00-17:50 谢天笑\n- 18:20-19:10 声音玩具\n- 19:40-20:40 唐朝乐队 (压轴)\n\n宋舞台:\n- 13:30-14:10 回春丹\n- 14:40-15:20 九宝乐队\n- 15:50-16:30 重塑雕像的权利\n- 17:00-17:50 刺猬乐队\n- 18:20-19:10 盘尼西林\n\n电子/嘻哈舞台:\n- 14:00-15:00 王以太\n- 15:30-16:30 Higher Brothers\n- 17:00-18:00 VAVA\n- 18:30-19:30 法老\n\n票价: 单日票 420元 / 三日通票 880元\n\n**Day 3: 7月20日 - 麦田音乐节 (Wheatfield Festival)**\n- 地点: (日期OCR未识别，推测7月20日)\n\n麦田舞台:\n- 14:00-14:40 棱镜乐队\n- 15:10-15:50 旅行团乐队\n- 16:20-17:00 银河系乐团\n- 17:30-18:20 EARS\n- 18:50-19:40 HAHA\n\n光年舞台 (暂名):\n- 14:00-14:40 Fine乐团\n- 15:10-15:50 焦迈奇\n- 16:20-17:00 颜人中\n- 17:30-18:20 夏日入侵企画\n- 18:50-19:40 郭顶\n\nBEE舞台 (暂名):\n- 14:30-15:10 Deca Joins\n- 15:40-16:20 老王乐队\n- 16:50-17:30 椅子乐团\n- 18:00-18:50 康姆士 COM'Z\n\n票价: 单日预售 280元 / 全价 380元 / VIP 580元\n\nWait, I need to reconsider the wheatfield poster. Looking at the OCR output again for the second stage